io functions
========================================================
Read *.his file into array
```{r}
workdir <- "d:\\MODELS\\ED\\"
modversion <- "eco-scen4-run1-28-y2_2-day"
modarr <- his2arr(paste(workdir, modversion, ".his", sep = ""))
dim(modarr)
```

io functions
========================================================
Convert array to dataframe
```{r}
subs <- c("Chlfa", "PO4")
locs = "WZ590_ZO_Lauwers_oos"
df <- arr2df(modarr, submod = subs, locmod = locs)
str(df)
```

Plot time series
========================================================
```{r, echo = F, fig.width = 15}
p <- ggplot(data = df, aes(x = time, y = value, color = variable))
p + geom_point(size = 3) + facet_grid(variable ~ ., scales = "free")
```
Result for `r locs`

Make Ecoplot
========================================================
```{r}
limmod = c("Limit e", "Limit nit", "Limit pho", "Limit sil")
locations = c("WZ590_ZO_Lauwers_oos")
DelwaqEcoplot(arr = modarr, locmod = locations, submod = "fPPtot", limmod = limmod, plottype = 1)
```
Result for `r locations`
Make Ecoplot (echo = FALSE)
========================================================

```{r, echo = F, fig.width = 15}
limmod = c("Limit e", "Limit nit", "Limit pho", "Limit sil")
locations = c("WZ590_ZO_Lauwers_oos")
(DelwaqEcoplot(arr = modarr, locmod = locations, submod = "fPPtot", limmod = limmod, plottype = 1))
```
Result for `r locations`

